Title: cmk-update-agent: Fix invalid signature error
Level: 1
Component: agents
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
Version: 1.4.0p12
Date: 1505299119
Class: fix

This werk fixes an issue occuring with the validation of the agent downloaded via cmk-update-agent:
When executing cmk-update-agent using curl for server communications, the script might abort with error message "invalid signature" and "no valid signature found"
